title: Ground News - Large fire burning near vehicle auto recycler north of Regina - Regina
text:
Summary by Ground News Fire crews are currently on scene as a large fire is ablaze near Bucks Auto Parts north of Regina . The cause of the blaze is not known at this time. Traffic is closed in both directions on Pasqua Street North, near Bucks auto Parts. Global News will bring you more as information becomes available. Share menu More
